fields.title: Children's Lotto

fields.name:
Type: lotto
Subject: animals, household, flowers

fields.historical_context_note:
No. of Players: 6
Equipment required: 6 large cards
54 small discs
original box

Rules:
sheet 1 - toys shown on a light blue background with illustrations of a drum, engine, trumpet, soldiers, doll, rocking horse, Noah's ark, ball, teddy bear
sheet 2 - animals, domestic and farm, shown on a green background with illustrations of a cat, dog, horse, lamb, rat, pig, rabbit, goat, donkey
sheet 3 - wild animals shown on a red background with illustrations of a monkey, lion, tiger, giraffe, elephant, zebra, bear, leopard and stag
sheet 4 - birds, shown on a yellow background with illustrations of a parrot, swallow, stork, ostrich, eagle, canary, owl, magpie and kingfisher
sheet 5 - household utensils shown on an orange background with illustrations of a teapot, kettle, saucepan, scales, watch, umbrella, book, radio and telephone
sheet 6 - fruit and vegetables shown on a pink background with illustrations of a potato, carrot, onion, cabbage, turnip, tomatoes, apple, orange, and grapes
